<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />I wash my hands in innocence,</para>

<para style="q1">and I go around your altar, Yahweh,</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />to sing a loud song of praise</para>

<para style="q1">and report all your wonderful deeds.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="8" style="v" />Yahweh, I love the house where you live,</para>

<para style="q1">the place where your glory lives!</para>
